Rating: 4
A simple marinade with great flavor. Like another reviewer I wanted to try out Costco's flap steak. I made this recipe twice. The rarer the better. I was confused by the long, narrow shape of the cut and sliced it with the grain the first time and it was tough (doh!). The second time I cut the steak into 8 inch pieces lengthwise then sliced across the grain. It was delicious!

