Rating: 4
I have made this recipe any number of times. I found that using good quality soy sauce(not salty Kikkoman),real maple syrup (not the corn syrup maple flavored type) and and aged balsamic vinegar will substantially improve the flavor. I think well worth the up-grade in ingredients.

